sql_json.natural_language: Pull the most recent email that has both brenda@statpackkzn.co.za and accounts@thegourmetgreek.com on it.
sql_json.generated_sql: SELECT messageId, threadId, fromEmail, subject, sentAt, snippet FROM email_search_index WHERE 'brenda@statpackkzn.co.za' IN UNNEST(toEmails) AND 'accounts@thegourmetgreek.com' IN UNNEST(toEmails) ORDER BY sentAt DESC LIMIT 1;
